      <title>习近平和普京获胜，更多亚洲领导人希望加入金砖国家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/more-asian-nations-want-to-join-putin-and-xi-in-expanded-brics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，俄罗斯总统普京和中国国务院总理李强分别在东南亚结束会晤之际，金砖国家经济集团的这两个合作伙伴遇到了一个渴望加入该组织的地区，该组织被视为对冲西方主导的机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/more-asian-nations-want-to-join-putin-and-xi-in-expanded-brics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 01:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杜特尔特继承人与马科斯决裂 彰显菲律宾雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/duterte-heir-signals-philippine-ambition-with-break-from-marcos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几周前，菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 曾对他的副手、副总统萨拉·杜特尔特 (Sara Duterte) 大加赞赏。随着杜特尔特本周辞去内阁职务，这位总统“永远最好的朋友”将成为他六年任期刚过两年的最强大挑战者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/duterte-heir-signals-philippine-ambition-with-break-from-marcos</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 00:46:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱重返欧洲，享受右翼选举的利好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/milei-basks-in-right-wing-election-gains-as-he-returns-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·米莱伊上次访问西班牙，却在试图影响欧洲选举的前夕引发了一场历史性的外交危机。受欧洲大陆右翼盟友成功的鼓舞，这位阿根廷总统现在又要再次访问西班牙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/milei-basks-in-right-wing-election-gains-as-he-returns-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:55:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>继美国和欧盟采取行动后，加拿大准备对中国电动汽车征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/canada-prepares-potential-tariffs-on-china-electric-vehicles-after-us-eu-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府正准备对中国制造的电动汽车征收新的关税，以使加拿大与美国和欧盟采取的行动保持一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/canada-prepares-potential-tariffs-on-china-electric-vehicles-after-us-eu-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰德·克鲁兹推动实施特朗普免税小费提案的法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/trump-s-tax-free-tips-idea-pushed-by-ted-cruz-in-new-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州参议员泰德·克鲁兹已提出法案，将唐纳德·特朗普提出的取消联邦小费税的提议纳入法典，此举驳斥了预算监督机构对此的担忧，后者担心此举可能导致十年内赤字增加 2500 亿美元甚至更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/trump-s-tax-free-tips-idea-pushed-by-ted-cruz-in-new-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:23:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
